message.content: cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.IR. The paper focuses on exploring the robustness and sensitivity of deep learning image classifiers through interactive manipulation of images. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the comparison and contrast of image regions used by humans and machine learning models for classification, which relates to the field of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper uses inpainting algorithms to modify images, which involves image retrieval (cs.IR) techniques. Finally, the paper discusses the resilience of deep learning models, which is a topic of interest in machine learning (cs.LG).
